title: IEEE Student Memberships Benefits
description: The session commenced with welcoming all FE students by the speaker Ajitha Rajkumar.Then the speaker why to join IEEE and explain its need in their social, technical part of engineering life.Speaker talked about new student resources available in the year 2021.Speaker discussed various IEEE sites such as students.ieee.org, ieee.xtreme.org, ieee-collabratec.ieee.org.Then speaker gave knowledge about the IEEE application.Speaker gave knowledge about volunteering opportunities IEEE.Then speaker told about the IEEE  DBIT student branch and its various activities carried throughout the year.Then they were told about a 50% discount on IEEE student membership which will be useful for them.Then there was a question and answer section in which all queries of participants were solved.The session was ended with a vote of thanks.
